Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.69,0:00:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那...那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,小夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算從今天開始住在這
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,總之請多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
